<plot>This is a profile of a family, shown through three Shabbat meals. A mother who is afraid to grow old, the older sister who wants someone to love her, the middle sister who wants to leave home, the younger sister who makes fun of them all, and the father who only wants to finish the meals in peace.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?357232</url></doc>
